        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer784599806" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16358811294810442507">10/10/19<br/>Was fun to revisit. Definitely has a completely different tone the the other in this duo. More aimed at a younger censored generation. Still fun. The complete lack of apprehension by the majority of the adults was a bit crazy but otherwise cool</span>

          </span>
        </div>


